<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<sample sampleID="LBi9_00078" version="1.0" type="fixedLength">
<article articleID="LBi9_00078_F001">
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「<sampling type="start" />今度こそおまえを殺してやる！</sentence>
<sentence>　友姫！」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「よせ、漁！」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「この顔を焼いたおまえ…！</sentence>
<sentence>　おまえのために今までどんな思いをしてきたか！</sentence>
<sentence>　同じように顔を焼いてやる！</sentence>
<sentence>　ひとを踏みつけにして、吉川の妻となった<ruby rubyText="ひ">卑</ruby><ruby rubyText="きょう">怯</ruby>な女！」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　タイミングが悪かった。</sentence>
<sentence>今の今まで見ていた過去の夢が、漁を衝動的な殺意に駆り立てた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「この手でその顔、焼いてやる！」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「鳴美！」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「ちょ…っ、やめなさい、漁姫！」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　手のひらを<ruby rubyText="しゃく">灼</ruby><ruby rubyText="ねつ">熱</ruby>に変えた漁が友姫に襲いかかったところに、綾子が間一髪、《<ruby rubyText="ねん">念</ruby><ruby rubyText="ぱ">波</ruby>》を撃ちはなつ…！</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「ぎゃっ！」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　悲鳴をあげて漁が吹っ飛ばされ、背後の壁に激突する。</sentence>
<sentence>あやうく顔を焼かれるところだった鳴美にさつきは駆け寄って背中にかばい込んだ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「鳴美に何しやがるんだよ！</sentence>
<sentence>　ねえさん！」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「…な…に」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　我にかえった漁は、すぐにそこにいた綾子らに気づいた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「誰じゃ、貴様！」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「<ruby rubyText="かき">柿</ruby><ruby rubyText="ざき">崎</ruby><ruby rubyText="はる">晴</ruby><ruby rubyText="いえ">家</ruby>。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">上杉の<ruby rubyText="や">夜</ruby><ruby rubyText="しゃ">叉</ruby><ruby rubyText="しゅう">衆</ruby>のひとりよ」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「上杉の…っ？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　驚いた顔で漁は綾子をまじまじと見た。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「上杉の方か。</sentence>
<sentence>どういうことだ。</sentence>
<sentence>なぜここにおられるのだ。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">これは」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「漁姫」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「なぜおまえがここにおるのだ、友姫！」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　漁はギラリと姉を<ruby rubyText="にら">睨</ruby>みつけた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「次に会うときは殺すと言ったはず。</sentence>
<sentence>何しに来た、そんなに殺されたかったか！」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「落ち着いて。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">それよりなにがあったの、漁姫」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　綾子はあわただしい口調で、</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「《吸力結界》がはってあったわ。</sentence>
<sentence>こんな真似ができるのは織田の森蘭丸くらいよ。</sentence>
<sentence>なにがあったの。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">まさか織田がここに」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　漁は気を失う前の出来事を思い出した。</sentence>
<sentence>唇を嚙み、しばらく悔しさに震えてから、漁はギラッとその後ろにいるさつきを睨んだ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「ひ…っ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　さつきは<ruby rubyText="おび">怯</ruby>えて綾子の背に隠れる。</sentence>
<sentence>さつきは自分がしたことを覚えていないのだ。</sentence>
<sentence>漁はそのままなお悔しげに奥歯を嚙みしめた。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「…『干珠』を、織田に奪われた」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「！」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「なんですって！」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「織田にはかられた。</sentence>
<sentence>お…のれぇ…。</sentence>
<sentence>奴らはじめから私をマークしていたのじゃ。</sentence>
<sentence>この者に催眠暗示をかけて『満珠』と『干珠』のことを聞き出しおった。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">不覚をとった…っ」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「あ、あたしが！</sentence>
<sentence>　そんな！」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　さつきはさっぱり覚えていない。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「じゃあ織田は―信長は『満珠』と『干珠』のこと全部知っちゃったの？</sentence>
<sentence>　あの珠の威力も！」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「騒ぐな！</sentence>
<sentence>　鹿之介様には迷惑はかけん。</sentence>
<sentence>私が取り返してやる。</sentence>
<sentence>あんな奴に踊らされてたまるものか！</sentence>
<sentence>　いまから厳島神社に斬り込んで、信長なんぞこの手で討ってやる！」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「慢心するな、漁！」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　ぴしゃり、と友姫が叱りつけたので、漁はビクンと肩を揺らした。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「そなたにどれほどのことができると思う！</sentence>
<sentence>　そなたなんぞが頭に血をのぼらせて斬り込んだところで、門番にでも討たれるのがおちじゃ！」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「な…なんじゃとォ！」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「そなたには、事の重大さがまったくわかっておらぬ！」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　友姫は<ruby rubyText="よう">容</ruby><ruby rubyText="しゃ">赦</ruby>なくハッキリ言った。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「織田信長なんぞの手に『満珠』と『干珠』が渡れば、もう毛利や尼子だけの問題では済まぬ。</sentence>
<sentence>やつらの手にあれが渡ったりなぞした<sampling type="end" />ら、日の本の制海権は織田に奪われるに違いない…！」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
</article>
</sample>
